precis:
Regulations Amending the CONTRAVENTIONS REGULATIONS by designating a number
of offences under the Wildlife Area Regulations and under the Migratory
Birds Regulations relating to the use of lead jigs and sinkers or lead-
containing shotgun cartridges (bullets), as contraventions that may be
disposed of by imposing a fine.
